## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-163">Autentifikavimo įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-163">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-164">Šie diagnostikos duomenų įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-164">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-165">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-165">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-166">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui formomis pagrįsto autentifikavimo prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-166">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-167">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, naudojami autentifikavimo raginimai siekiant nustatyti, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama. Tai vartotojui iš esmės reiškia, kad kliento būsena bus Neprisijungęs, arba, blogiausiu atveju, dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir bus visiškai negalima naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-167">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts is used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-168">Formomis pagrįsto autentifikavimo (FBA) prisijungimo raginimai naudojami kai kuriais vietinio autentifikavimo scenarijais ir paprastai norime įsitikinti, kad tai nevyksta, nes visi turėtų naudoti šiuolaikinį autentifikavimą dėl su FBA siejamų saugos pažeidžiamumų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-168">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn’t happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-169">**Renkami šių laukų duomenys:**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-169">**The following fields are collected:**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-170">**AuthScheme** – naudojama autentifikavimo schema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-170">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-171">**DocumentUrlHash** – prašomas užšifruotas URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-171">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-172">**EndTag** – FBA formos pabaigos žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-172">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-173">**Flags** – nebenaudojama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-173">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-174">**FlowTag** – FBA formos pradžios žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-174">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-175">**LastError** – pateiktas klaidos kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-175">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-176">**PromptEndTime** – raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-176">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-177">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-177">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-178">**Result** – ar autentifikavimas sėkmingas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-178">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-179">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-179">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-180">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-180">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-181">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-181">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-182">Renkama, kai vartotojas atsijungia nuo „Office“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-182">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-183">Žinant, kad vartotojas atsijungė, galima klasifikuoti kitus įvykius, pvz., raginimus, kaip numatyta, kad šie įvykiai būtų tinkamai apskaičiuoti patikimumo / parengimo pateikti metrikoje ir būtų išvengta įspėjimų arba komponavimo versijų keitimų atšaukimo darant klaidingą prielaidą, kad vartotojui pateikiami netikėti prisijungimo raginimai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-183">Knowing the user is signed-out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-184">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-184">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-185">**FlowEndTime** – atsijungimo veiksmo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-185">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-186">**FlowStartTime** – atsijungimo veiksmo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-186">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-187">**IdentityErrorState** – bet kokia tapatybės klaidos būsena atsijungiant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-187">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-188">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** – užšifruotas tapatybės ID, kurio atsijungimo procesas vykdomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-188">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-189">**IdentityProviderType** – tapatybės, kurios atsijungimo procesas vykdomas, tapatybės teikėjas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-189">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-190">**IdentityUniqueID** – tapatybės ID, kurio atsijungimo procesas vykdomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-190">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-191">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-191">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-192">**SignOutUserAction** – nurodo, kad vartotojas inicijuoja atsijungimo veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-192">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-193">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-193">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-194">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui „Windows“ SSPI prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-194">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-195">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, autentifikavimo raginimai lemia, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama (dėl jos kliento būsena tampa Neprisijungęs).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-195">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-196">Dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir gali visiškai nepavykti naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-196">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-197">„Windows“ SSPI raginimai naudojami autentifikuojant per „Exchange“ (el. paštui sinchronizuoti), kai vartotojo „Exchange“ išteklius nebuvo nustatytas naudoti kelių dalių autentifikavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-197">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been setup for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-198">Šie įvykiai, kartu su „Office.MATS“ vardų srities įvykiais, naudojami šiais tikslais:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-198">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-199">1\) Siekiant nustatyti, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-199">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-200">2\) Siekiant įvertinti, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-200">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-201">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-201">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-202">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių vartotojams dirbti neleidžiančių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-202">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-203">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-203">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-204">**AllowSavedCreds** – ar nauji kredencialai išlaikomi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-204">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-205">**AuthScheme** – naudojama autentifikavimo schema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-205">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-206">**CredsSaved** – ar nauji kredencialai įrašomi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-206">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-207">**DocumentUrlHash** – prašomas užšifruotas URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-207">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-208">**EndTag** – raginimo pabaigos žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-208">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-209">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – ar nauja tapatybė yra galiojanti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-209">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-210">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** – užšifruotas naujas tapatybės ID užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-210">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-211">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – naujas tapatybės teikėjas užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-211">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-212">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – naujas tapatybės ID užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-212">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-213">**OutStatus** – ar raginimo išvestis yra galiojanti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-213">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-214">**PromptEndTime** - raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-214">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-215">**PromptFailedTag** – žymė, nurodanti SSPI raginimo triktį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-215">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-216">**PromptFlow** – žymė, kuri iškvietė SSPI raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-216">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-217">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-217">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-218">**Proxy** – ar naudojamas tarpinis serveris</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-218">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-219">**ServerHash** – užšifruotas serverio adresas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-219">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-220">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-220">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-221">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-221">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-222">**UiMessage** – vartotojo sąsajos pranešimas raginime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-222">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-223">**UserNameHash** – užšifruotas vartotojo vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-223">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitywin32prompt"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-224">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-224">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-225">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui kelių dalių autentifikavimo prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-225">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-226">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, autentifikavimo raginimai lemia, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama (dėl jos kliento būsena tampa Neprisijungęs).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-226">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-227">Dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir gali visiškai nepavykti naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-227">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-228">Šie įvykiai, kartu su „Office.MATS“ vardų srities įvykiais, naudojami šiais tikslais:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-228">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-229">1\) Siekiant nustatyti, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-229">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered in to a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-230">2\) Siekiant įvertinti, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-230">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-231">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-231">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-232">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių vartotojams dirbti neleidžiančių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-232">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-233">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-233">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-234">**AdalWAMUsed** – žymė, kuri nurodo rezultatą, jei naudojamas ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-234">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-235">**CallTag** – žymė, kuri nurodo, kas iškviečia prisijungimo vartotojo sąsają</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-235">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-236">**Context** – raginimo prisijungimo kontekstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-236">**Context** - the sign in context for the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-237">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** – žymė, kur prašomas tapatybės teikėjas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-237">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-238">**HrdShownTag** – žymė, kur rodomas HRD prisijungimo dialogo langas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-238">**HrdShownTag** - the tag where the HRD sign in dialog is shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-239">**IdentityProviderResulted** – prašomas tapatybės teikėjo tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-239">**IdentityProviderResulted** - the identity provider type it is requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-240">**IdPFlowTag** – žymė, kuri nurodo tapatybės užklausos rezultatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-240">**IdPFlowTag** - the tag that indicates the identity request result</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-241">**LastLoginDelta** – laiko pokytis nuo paskutinio sėkmingo prisijungimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-241">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-242">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** – ar tapatybė galioja po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-242">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** - whether the identity is valid after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-243">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – naujas tapatybės teikėjo tipas po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-243">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider type after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-244">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – naujas tapatybės ID, pateiktas po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-244">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID returned after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-245">**PromptCorrelation** – raginimo sąsajos ID diagnostikos tikslais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-245">**PromptCorrelation** - the prompt correlation ID for diagnostic purpose</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-246">**PromptEndTime** - raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-246">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-247">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-247">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-248">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-248">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-249">**ShowUIResult** – rezultato kodas, pateiktas iš raginimo vartotojo sąsajos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-249">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-250">**StartTag** – žymė, kur pradėtas „Win32“ raginimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-250">**StartTag** – the tag where Win32 prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-251">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-251">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-252">**WasIdentitySignedOut** – ar vartotojas atsijungęs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-252">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - whether the user is signed out</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-253">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-253">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-254">Tolesnis aprašas taikomas ir „Win32“, ir „WinRT“ įvykiams (pavadinimas priklauso nuo platformos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-254">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-255">„Microsoft“ autentifikavimo telemetrijos sistemos (MATS) įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-255">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-256">Kai bandymas gauti nepavyksta, įtraukiama klaidos informacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-256">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-257">Šie įvykiai padeda vartotojams išvengti netinkamos autentifikavimo būsenos:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-257">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-258">1\) Nustatant, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-258">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-259">2\) Įvertinant, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-259">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-260">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-260">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-261">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-261">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-262">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-262">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-263">**Actiontype** – kuri autentifikavimo biblioteka naudojama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-263">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-268">**Askedforcreds** – ar programa paprašė vartotojo įvesti kredencialus atliekant šį veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-268">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-270">**Blockingprompt** – ar programa pateikė raginimą, reikalaujantį vartotojo sąveikos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-270">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-275">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anoniminis įrenginio ID, naudojamas vertinant įrenginio patirtį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-275">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-347">**Scenarioid** – GUID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-347">**Scenarioid** – GUID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-348">Vienam scenarijui gali priklausyti keli įvykiai, pvz., scenarijus gali įtraukti naują paskyrą, bet vykstant tam scenarijui pateikiami keli raginimai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-348">Multiple events may belong to a single scenario, e.g. the scenario may be adding a new account but there are multiple prompts that occur as part of that scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-349">Šis ID įgalina sąsają.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-349">This ID enables correlation to happen.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-350">**Sessionid** – GUID, identifikuojantis įkrovos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-350">**Sessionid** - GUID identifying the boot session</span></span>

## <a name="click-to-run-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-358">Spustelėkite ir naudokitės įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-358">Click-to-Run events</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-359">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-359">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-360">„Office“ sąrankos ir aprašų duomenys, renkami vartotojui paleidus „Office“ setup.exe, kad modifikuotų įdiegtus „Office“ produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-360">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-361">Naudojami vertinant viso vartotojo inicijuoto „Office“ diegimo sėkmingumą, įskaitant būtinąsias patikras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-361">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-362">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-362">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-363">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – įvykusios klaidos kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-363">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-364">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcija, kurios klaida įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-364">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-365">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – įkėlimo įrankio dalis, kurioje įvyko klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-365">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-366">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – išimties tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-366">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-367">**Data\_Culture** – kultūra, su kuria vykdomas šis „exe“, pvz., „en-us“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-367">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-368">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – atpažinimo ženklo SHA-256 maiša, kurią mums nurodo OLS paslauga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-368">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-369">**Data\_Platform** – „x64“ arba „x86“ įdiegtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-369">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-370">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – įvykusi būtinųjų sąlygų triktis, pvz., nepalaikoma operacinė sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-370">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, ie. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-371">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – diegiamas produktas, pvz., „Office 365 ProPlus“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-371">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we’re installing, i.e. Office 365 ProPlus</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-372">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-372">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-373">„Office“ sąrankos ir inventoriaus duomenys, renkami Spustelėkite ir naudokitės klientui vykdant patikrą dėl sugadinimo, siekiant įsitikinti, kad „Office“ dvejetainiai failai yra teisingi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-373">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-374">Naudojami vertinant, ar „Office“ dvejetainiai failai yra sugadinti ir kurie dvejetainiai failai yra sugadinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-374">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-375">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-376">**Data\_Active –** dabartinė srauto deklaracija, kurią tikriname diske</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-376">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we’re checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-377">**Data\_ActivePackages –** kokie paketai yra deklaracijoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-377">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-378">**Data\_ActiveVersion –** deklaracijos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-378">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-379">**Data\_AddFileCount –** kiek failų įtraukiame</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-379">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we’re adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-380">**Data\_AddFileFiles –** įtraukiamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-380">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we’re adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-381">**Data\_CompressionLevel –** kaip failai suglaudinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-381">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-382">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel –** kaip nuodugniai tikriname dėl sugadinimo (etapai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-382">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we’re checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-383">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount –** kelių failų dydis yra sugadintas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-383">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount -** how many files have a corrupt size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-384">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles –** failų, kurių dydis sugadintas, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-384">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-385">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount –** kelių failų versija sugadinta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-385">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount -** how many files have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-386">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles –** failų, kurių versija sugadinta, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-386">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-387">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount –** kiek failų nepavyko atidaryti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-387">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount -** how many files we failed to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-388">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles –** failų, kurių nepavyko atidaryti, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-388">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles -** a sample of the files that we were unable to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-389">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount –** kiek failų nėra pasirašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-389">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount -** have many files that aren’t signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-390">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles –** failų, kurie nėra pasirašyti, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-390">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles -** a sample of the files that aren’t signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-391">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount –** kiek failų nėra patikimi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-391">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount -** how many files aren’t trusted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-392">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles –** nepatikimų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-392">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles -** a sample of the files that we don’t trust</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-393">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount –** kiek failų atrodo nepilni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-393">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount -** how many files seem to be incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-394">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles –** nepilnų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-394">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-395">**Data\_KeepFileCount –** dėl kiek failų nieko nedaroma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-395">**Data\_KeepFileCount -** how many files we’re not doing anything to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-396">**Data\_KeepFileFiles –** paliekamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-396">**Data\_KeepFileFiles -** a sample of files we’re keeping</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-397">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount –** kiek failų nekeičiama, nepaisant to, kad jie yra nepilni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-397">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount -** how many files we’re not changing despite them being incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-398">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles –** paliekamų nepilnų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-398">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files we’re keeping that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-399">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount –** kelių failų dydis neatitinka mūsų deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-399">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount -** how many files have a size that doesn’t match our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-400">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles –** failų, kurių dydis neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-400">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that are mismatched in size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-401">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount –** kelių failų versija skiriasi nuo mūsų deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-401">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount -** how many files that have a version different than our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-402">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles –** failų, kurių versijos neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-402">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have mismatched versions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-403">**Data\_MissingFileCount –** kiek failų trūksta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-403">**Data\_MissingFileCount -** how many files seem to be missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-404">**Data\_MissingFileFiles –** trūkstamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-404">**Data\_MissingFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-405">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount –** kiek failų neperduodama srautu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-405">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount -** how many files we’re not streaming</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-406">**Data\_RemoveFileCount –** kiek failų šalinama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-406">**Data\_RemoveFileCount -** how many files we’re removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-407">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles –** šalinamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-407">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles -** a sample of the files we’re removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-408">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount –** kiek failų vienetų neatitinka deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-408">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount -** how many files have units that don’t match the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-409">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles –** failų, kurių srauto vienetai neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-409">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles -** a sample of the files that have a stream with units mismatched</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-410">**Data\_TimeElapsed –** kiek užtruko patikra dėl sugadinimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-410">**Data\_TimeElapsed -** how long we took to check for corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-411">**Data\_UpdateFileCount –** kiek failų naujiname</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-411">**Data\_UpdateFileCount -** how many files we’re updating</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-413">**Data\_Working –** nauja tikrinama deklaracija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-413">**Data\_Working -** the new manifest we’re checking</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-414">**Data\_WorkingVersion –** naujos deklaracijos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-414">**Data\_WorkingVersion -** the version of the new manifest</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunmachinemetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-415">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-415">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-417">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-417">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-420">**Data\_OfficeVersion** – sistemos, kurioje įdiegtas „Office“, versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-420">**Data\_OfficeVersion** - The version Office is installed in</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunodt"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-423">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-423">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-424">„Office“ sąrankos ir inventoriaus duomenys, renkami, kai IT administratorius vykdo „Office“ diegimo įrankio Spustelėkite ir naudokitės setup.exe, kad modifikuotų vartotojų įdiegtus „Office“ produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-424">Office set up and inventory data collected when an IT Admin is running the Office Deployment Tool Click-to-Run setup.exe to modify their users’ installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-425">Naudojamas vertinant visų IT administratoriaus inicijuotų „Office“ diegimų sėkmingumą, įskaitant būtinųjų sąlygų patikras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-425">It is used to measure success / failure of full IT Admin initiated Office installations including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-426">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-426">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-443">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-443">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-444">Ataskaitos apie naujo spustelėkite ir naudokitės naujinimo srauto būseną ("Repoman") ir, jei ji sėkmingai atsisiunčia ir pritaiko "Office" naujinimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-444">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline (“Repoman”) and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-447">**DownloadSucceeded –** tiesa, jei srautui sėkmingai pritaikytas „Office“ naujinys, klaidinga, jei ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-447">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-448">**ErrorCode –** paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-448">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-449">**ErrorDetails –** papildoma paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, informacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-449">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-450">**ErrorMessage –** paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, pranešimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-450">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-451">**Openstreamsessionpavyko –** teisinga, jei srautas sėkmingai sukuria seansą, skirtą „Office“ naujiniui transliuoti, klaidinga, jei ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-451">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1409">„Office“ sąrankos ir inventoriaus duomenys, renkami, kai Spustelėkite ir naudokitės klientas kuria perdavimo srautą, kad atsisiųstų „Office“ failus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1409">Office set up and inventory data collected when the Click-to-Run client is creating a transport stream to download Office files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1410">Naudojami nustatant įvairių perdavimo technologijų (pvz., HTTP, BITS, DO) sveikatą. Tai svarbu, kad „Office“ būtų tinkamai atsisiųsta diegiant ir naujinant.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1410">Used for determining the health of various transport technologies (e.g., HTTP, BITS, DO) which is critical to downloading Office properly for installation and updates.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1508">**DeliveryMechanism –** „FFNRoot“ guid, išgaunamas iš „Version Descriptor XML“ (įspaustas RDX), kuriame nurodoma, iš kokios auditorijos/kanalo gautas komponavimo šaltinis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1508">**DeliveryMechanism –**   The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1514">\*\*ExitCode – \*\*sveikoji reikšmė, susieta su „bootstrapper“ paleidimo fazės rezultatu, rodanti sėkmingus bandymus ir tam tikrų tipų triktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1514">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1517">**PreReqResult –** sveikojo skaičiaus išvardijimo reikšmė, kai buvo atlikti „PreReq“ tikrinimai (pavyko/nepavyko/paleisti iš naujo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1517">**PreReqResult –**    The integer enum value of the result when PreReq checks were performed (pass/fail/re-run)</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationflightnumberline"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1527">Office.Experimentation.FlightNumberLine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1527">Office.Experimentation.FlightNumberLine</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationtriggeranalysis"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1535">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1535">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1536">Šis įvykis padeda analizuoti produkto naudojimą ir veikimo metriką (pvz., triktis, užstrigimus ir t. t.) į vartotojų arba įrenginių, kurie gali naudoti funkciją, pogrupį ir taip padeda užtikrinti, kad produktas veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1536">This event helps scope analysis of product usage and performance metrics (such as crashes, hangs, etc.) to the subset of users or devices that are eligible to use the feature, thereby helping ensure that the product is working properly.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1538">**FeatureGate –** nurodo funkcijų, kurioms galima taikyti analizę, rinkinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1538">**FeatureGate -** Identifies the set of features for which the trigger analysis is applicable.</span></span>

## <a name="licensing-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1539">Licencijavimo įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1539">Licensing events</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingaccepteulaforcurrentlicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1540">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1540">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1541">Renkami, kai vartotojas licencijuojamas ir sutinka su dabartinės licencijos GVLS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1541">This is collected when the user gets licensed and accepts EULA for the current license</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1542">Jie naudojami nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama, taip pat sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1542">It is used to detect if the user is in a good state or not, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1543">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1543">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1544">**ACID** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1544">**ACID** - A GUID identifier representing the office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1545">**DwEulaId** – GVLS, su kuriomis vartotojas ką tik sutiko, tipo skaitinis identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1545">**DwEulaId** – Numeric identifier of the type of EULA that was just accepted by the user</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivation"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1546">Office.Licensing.Activation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1546">Office.Licensing.Activation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1547">Nustatę licenciją kompiuteryje, bandome suaktyvinti licenciją iškviesdami AVS paslaugą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1547">Post setting up the license on the machine, we attempt to activate the license by calling the AVS service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1548">Tai praneša apie aktyvinimo iškvietimo rezultatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1548">This reports the result of the activation call</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1549">Svarbu nustatyti, kiek vartotojų turi aktyvinimo problemų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1549">It is critical in detecting how many users are facing activation issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1550">Anomalijų aptikimo funkcija aptinka suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1550">We have anomaly detection to detect any regression.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1551">Tai ypač svarbu, nes yra išorinė priklausomybė nuo AVS ir šis signalas nurodo, ar mūsų išorinių partnerių būklė yra gera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1551">This is super critical as we have an external dependency on AVS and this signal points whether our external partners are healthy .</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1552">Tai taip pat naudojama diagnostikos ir sistemos sveikatos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1552">It is also used for diagnostic purposes and system health if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1553">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1553">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1554">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1554">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1555">**ReferralData** – OĮG, kuris įdiegė „Office“ kompiuteryje, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1555">**ReferralData** – Identifier of the OEM that installed office on the machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingloadidentityticket"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1627">Office.Licensing.LoadIdentityTicket</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1627">Office.Licensing.LoadIdentityTicket</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1647">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1647">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1648">**MetadataValidationResult** – licencijos metaduomenų patikrinimo, siekiant patvirtinti, kad licencija nėra piktavališkai pakeista, rezultatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1648">**MetadataValidationResult** – Result of the validation of the metadata of the license to verify that it has not been tampered with</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingnulvalidationfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1650">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1650">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1651">Renkama kiekviename įrenginio, kuriam taikomas šiuolaikinis licencijavimo procesas, seanse.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1651">This is collected on every session of a device that is running on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1652">Pranešama kompiuterio licencijavimo būsena ir vartotojo matomos klaidos, dėl kurių jis negali naudoti programos. Šis įvykis nurodo, ar vartotojo kompiuterio sveikata šiuolaikiniame licencijavimo procese yra gera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1652">It reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the app This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1653">Šio įvykio anomalijų aptikimo funkcija nurodo, ar netinkamą vartotojo elgseną kelia veikimo suprastėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1653">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1654">Tai taip pat svarbu diagnozuojant vartotojo problemas ir stebint sistemos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1654">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1655">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1655">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1656">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1656">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1657">**AllAcids** – visų produkto, kurio licenciją vartotojas šiuo metu turi, GUID sąrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1657">**AllAcids** – List of all the GUIDs of the product that the user is currently licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1658">**Category** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1658">**Category** - Category of the office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1659">**DaysRemaining** – iki dabartinės „Office“ licencijos galiojimo pabaigos likusių dienų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1659">**DaysRemaining** – Number of days remaining before the current office license expires</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1660">**LicenseId** – vartotojui išduotos licencijos iš raidžių ir skaitmenų sudarytas identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1660">**LicenseId** – An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1661">**LicenseType** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1661">**LicenseType** - Type of the office license that the user is using</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingofficeclientlicensingdolicensevalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1662">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1662">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1663">Licencijavimo metaduomenys, renkami iš įrenginio per kiekvieną įkrovą, kurie praneša licencijos ACID, licencijos būseną, tipą ir kitas licencijos ypatybes, kurios svarbios identifikuojant vartotojui pasiekiamų funkcijų rinkinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1663">This is licensing metadata that is collected from the device on every boot that reports the license acid, license status, type and other properties of the license that are critical in identifying the features set available to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1664">Tai svarbu identifikuojant vartotojui pasiekiamų funkcijų rinkinį ir vartotojui trūkstamas funkcijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1664">This is critical in identifying the feature set available to the user and if any functionality is missing for the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1665">Tai taip pat naudojama apskaičiuojant dienos / mėnesio aktyvių vartotojų skaičių ir pateikiant įvairias kitas ataskaitas įvairioms „Office“ komandoms, nes tai praneša vartotojo naudojamo produkto tipą, ar tai produkto prenumerata ir ar jam netrūksta svarbių funkcijų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1665">It is also used for Daily active users/Monthly active user calculations and various other reports by various teams across office(marketing/DIG/licensing) as this tells the type product that the user is using, whether it is a subscription product and whether they are missing any critical functionality.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1666">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1666">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1667">**FullValidationMode** – režimas, nurodantis, kad vykdomas išsamus licencijos patikrinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1667">**FullValidationMode** – Mode indicating that we are in full validation of license verification</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1668">**IsRFM** – nurodo, ar vartotojas dirba sumažinto funkcionalumo režimu, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1668">**IsRFM** – Indicates whether the user is in reduced functionality mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1669">**IsSCA** – nurodoma, ar veikia bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio aktyvinimo režimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1669">**IsSCA** – Indicates whether we are running in Shared computer activation mode</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1670">**IsSubscription** – nurodo, ar vartotojas naudoja prenumeratos licenciją, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1670">**IsSubscription** – Indicates whether the user is using a subscription license or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1671">**IsvNext** – nurodo ar naudojame naują šiuolaikinį licencijavimo procesą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1671">**IsvNext** – Indicates whether we are using the new modern licensing stack or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1672">**LicenseCategory** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1672">**LicenseCategory** - Category of the office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1673">**LicenseStatus** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1673">**LicenseStatus** – Status of the office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1674">**LicenseType** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1674">**LicenseType** - Type of the office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1675">**LicensingACID** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1675">**LicensingACID** - A GUID identifier representing the office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1676">**OlsLicenseId** – vartotojui išduotos licencijos iš raidžių ir skaitmenų sudarytas identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1676">**OlsLicenseId** - An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1677">**SkuIdIsNull** – nurodo, ar įvyko klaida ir nežinome, kokį produktą naudoja vartotojas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1677">**SkuIdIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered an error and don’t know the product that the user is running</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1678">**SlapiIsNull** – nurodo, ar kilo problema kuriant vieną iš licencijavimo objektų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1678">**SlapiIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered a problem in populating one of the licensing objects</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingskutoskuconversion"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1702">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1702">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1703">Jei licencijuodami vartotoją turime pakeisti vartotojo SKU iš vieno SKU į kitą, išsiunčiame šį signalą kartu su sėkmingo įvykdymo arba trikties kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1703">As part of licensing the user, if we have to change the user's SKU from one SKU to another, we send this signal out along with the success or failure code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1704">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1704">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1705">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1705">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1706">**DestinationSku** – SKU, į kurį turi būti konvertuotas šiuo metu įdiegtas produktas, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1706">**DestinationSku** – Name of the SKU to which the currently installed product should be converted to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1707">**PendingAcid** – produkto, kurio SKU konvertavimas laukia, ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1707">**PendingAcid** – Id of the product for which a SKU conversion is pending</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1708">**SourceSku** – pradinio SKU, kuris buvo įdiegtas kompiuteryje, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1708">**SourceSku** – Name of the original SKU that was installed on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1709">**UninstallProduct** – nurodo, ar senasis produktas bus pašalintas konvertuojant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1709">**UninstallProduct** – Indicates whether the old product will be uninstalled as part of the conversion</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingusegracekey"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1710">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1710">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1711">Jei dėl kokios nors priežasties nepavyksta licencijuoti vartotojo, įdiegiame atidėjimo raktą ir išsiunčiame šį signalą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1711">For some reason if we are unable to license the user, we install a grace key and send out this signal that signifies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1712">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1712">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1713">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1713">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1714">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – nurodo, ar bandėme oportunistiškai atnaujinti vartotojui bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio aktyvinimo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1714">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates if we attempted an opportunistic renewal for the user in shared computer activation mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1715">**ReArmResult** – nurodo įdiegto rakto, kuris gali pratęsti dabartinės licencijos galiojimą, pradinės licencijavimo būsenos atkūrimo rezultatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1715">**ReArmResult** – Indicates the result of rearming the installed key which can extend the expiry of the current license</span></span>

## <a name="microsoft-autoupdate-mau-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1716">„Microsoft AutoUpdate“ (MAU) įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1716">Microsoft AutoUpdate (MAU) events</span></span>

### <a name="appdelegate_launch"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-1717">appdelegate_launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1717">appdelegate_launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-1718">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad įvyko mėginimas įjungti taikomąją programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1718">This event denotes that an attempt to launch the app occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1719">Užregistruojame jo rezultatą (nesėkmė arba sėkmė).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1719">We log its result (failure or success).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1720">Šis įvykis naudojamas nustatyti atvejus, kai MAU nepavyksta paleisti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1720">We use this event to identify cases in which MAU fails to launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1724">**AppversionLong** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1724">**AppversionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1725">**Channel** – auditorijos pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1725">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1726">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1726">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1727">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1727">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1728">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1728">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1729">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1729">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1730">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1730">**OsMinorVer -** The Minor version of the Operating System.</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1731">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1731">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1732">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1732">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1733">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1733">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1734">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1734">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1735">**Payload** – statinio teksto, nurodančios paleisties būseną, rinkinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1735">**Payload** - A set of static text indicating launch status.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1736">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1736">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1737">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji 3 IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1737">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-1738">**SessionId** – seanso identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-1738">**SessionId** - The globally unique identifier for the host’s session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-2837">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad atsisiuntimo agentas nukreiptas į galinį punktą, kuris nurodo atsisiuntimo užklausos URL peradresavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2837">This event denotes that the downloader agent is pointed to an endpoint that issues a URL redirect for the download request.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2838">Šis įvykis naudojamas norint išaiškinti nepavykusį atsisiuntimą ir diagnozuoti tarpinio serverio triktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2838">We use this even to explain reasons for download failure and diagnose proxy issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2839">Jis taip pat gali padėti diagnozuoti priežastis, kodėl vartotojai diegia senesnes versijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2839">It can also help diagnose reasons why users are observed to install older builds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2840">Šis įvykis naudojamas, kad būtų užtikrinta, jog naujinimo procesas veikia taip, kaip tikėtasi, ir padėti pašalinti klaidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2840">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2850">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2850">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2851">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2851">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2852">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2852">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2853">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2853">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2854">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2854">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2855">**Payload** – yra peradresuotas URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2855">**Payload** - Contains redirected URL.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2856">Tai yra „Microsoft“ atsisiuntimo vieta, išskyrus atvejus, kai kanalas nustatytas kaip Pasirinktinis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2856">This is Microsoft download location except when the channel is set to Custom.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-2857">Pasirinktiniame kanale ši reikšmė nustatyta kaip „Pasirinktinė vieta“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-2857">For Custom channel, this value is set to "Custom Location".</span></span>
