- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5292">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5292">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5293">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5293">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5294">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5294">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5295">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5295">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5296">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5296">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5297">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5297">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5298">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5298">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5299">**Payload** – yra žiniatinklio tarnybos skambintojo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5299">**Payload** - Contains web-service caller ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5300">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5300">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5301">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji 3 IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5301">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-5303">„OneNote“ sinchronizavimo įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5303">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-5304">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5304">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="bf211-5305">Šis įvykis registruoja bloknoto sinchronizavimo rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5305">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5306">Jis naudojamas norint suprasti, kiek reikia unikalių sinchronizavimo tikslų, apskaičiuojant „OneNote“ sinchronizavimo balą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5306">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5308">**CachedError_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti talpyklinės klaidos pobūdį ir (arba), kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5308">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5309">**CachedError_Description** – talpyklinės klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5309">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5310">**CachedError_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta talpyklinė klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5310">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5311">**CachedError_Type** – talpyklinės klaidos tipas, pvz., „Win32Error“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5311">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5312">**ExecutionTime** – laikas milisekundėmis, reikalingas bloknotui dubliuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5312">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5313">**Gosid** – visuotinio objekto srities ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5313">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5314">**IdentityType** – tapatybės tipas, pavyzdžiui, „Windows Live“, organizacijos ID ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5314">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5317">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar talpyklinė klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5317">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5318">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar talpyklinė klaida netikėta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5318">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5319">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5319">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5320">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida netikėta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5320">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5321">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5321">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5322">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5322">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5323">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – nurodo, ar bloknotas sinchronizuotas naudojant šiuolaikinį puslapio turinio sinchronizavimą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5323">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5324">**LastAttemptedSync** – laiko žyma, nurodanti, kada bloknotas buvo bandytas sinchronizuoti paskutinį kartą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5324">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5326">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – vėliausios bloknoto peržiūros data</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5326">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5327">**LastSuccessfulSync** – laiko žyma, nurodanti, kada bloknotas buvo sėkmingai sinchronizuotas prieš tai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5327">**LastSuccessfulSync** – timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5328">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – nurodo, ar sinchronizavimą reikia paleisti iš naujo dėl nesuderinamumų, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5328">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5329">**NotebookErrorCode** – nurodo, kad bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaidos kodas įrašytas bloknoto diagramos srityje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5329">**NotebookErrorCode** – notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5330">**NotebookId** – bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5330">**NotebookId** – notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5331">**NotebookType** – bloknoto tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5331">**NotebookType** – notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5332">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – nurodo, ar sinchronizavimas paleidžiamas iš naujo dėl nesuderinamumų, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5332">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5333">**SectionError_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaidos pobūdį ir (arba) kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5333">**SectionError_Code** – a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5334">**SectionError_Description** – sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5334">**SectionError_Description** – a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5335">**SectionError_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5335">**SectionError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5336">**SectionError_Type** – sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaidos tipas, pvz., „Win32Error“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5336">**SectionError_Type** – the type of the section sync error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5337">**Success** – nurodo, ar bloknotą pavyko sėkmingai sinchronizuoti, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5337">**Success** – is the notebook sync successful or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5338">**SyncDestinationType** – nurodo sinchronizacijos paskirties tipą, pvz., „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint Online“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5338">**SyncDestinationType** – sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-5345">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5345">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="bf211-5346">Šis įvykis registruoja „WebSocket“ sinchronizavimo rezultatus, kad OneNot" moderniame puslapyje turinys būtų sinchronizuojamas šiuolaikiška hierarchija. Jis naudojamas norint suprasti, kiek yra unikalių sinchronizavimo tikslų, apskaičiuojant „OneNote“ sinchronizavimo balą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5346">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5347">Jis taip pat naudojamas „OneNote“ modernių sinchronizavimo efektyvumo ataskaitų srityje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5347">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="bf211-5348">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5348">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5349">**CloseReason** – „Web Socket“ uždarymo priežastis, pvz., nenormalus uždarymas ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5349">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5350">**DataIsFreshCount** – sėkmingų užklausų iš „Web Socket“ seanso skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5350">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5351">**DeviceSessionId** – įrenginio seanso ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5351">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5352">**DownloadCount** – Atsisiuntimų skaičius „Web Socket“ seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5352">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5353">**Error** – yra iš esmės Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5353">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5354">**Exception_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti klaidos pobūdį ir (arba), kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5354">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5355">**Exception_Description** – trumpas klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5355">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5356">**Exception_Tag** – nurodo vietą kode, kur yra klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5356">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5357">**Exception_Type** – klaidos tipas, pvz. Win32Error ir t.t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5357">**Exception_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5358">**FirstUpdateSize** – pirmo atnaujinimo pranešimo ilgis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5358">**FirstUpdateSize** - first update message length</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5359">**HasError** – ar įvyko klaida „Web Socket“ seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5359">**HasError** - whether there is an error during the WebSocket session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5360">**IsEducationNotebook** – ar dabartinis bloknotas yra išsilavinimo bloknotas, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5360">**IsEducationNotebook** - Is the current notebook education notebook or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5361">**IsHierarchyResource** – ar dabartiniai ištekliai yra puslapyje, ar sekcijoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5361">**IsHierarchyResource** - Is the current resource a page or a section</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5362">**NotebookId** – „OneNote“ bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5362">**NotebookId** - OneNote notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5363">**OperationWithError** – kurios operacijos metu įvyko klaida, pvz., WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open ir t.t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5363">**OperationWithError** - in which operation did the error happen, e.g. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5364">**ResourceId** – „OneNote“ puslapio arba skyriaus išteklių ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5364">**ResourceId** - OneNote page or section resource ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5365">**SectionId** – „OneNote“ skyriaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5365">**SectionId** - OneNote section ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5366">**ServerSessionId** – seanso ID, naudojamas susieti „WebSocket“ prašymą su onenote.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5366">**ServerSessionId** - session ID used to correlate WebSocket request to onenote.com</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5367">**SessionDurationInMs** – „WebSocket“ seanso trukmė milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5367">**SessionDurationInMs** - the duration in milliseconds of the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5402">**TenantId** – „SharePoint“ nuomotojo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5402">**TenantId** - SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5413">**Error_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5413">**Error_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5414">**Error_Type** – klaidos tipas, pvz., „Win32Error“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5414">**Error_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5417">**fishbowlType** – „Fishbowl“ tipas pvz., Page Fishbowl, Section Fishbowl ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5417">**fishbowlType** - type of fishbowl, e.g. page fishbowl, section fishbowl, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5419">**idsFishbowl** – vartotojo sąsajos rodomas „Fishbowl“ klaidos sveikasis identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5419">**idsFishbowl** - an integer identifier for the fishbowl error shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5420">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** – ar naudoja modernų hierarchinį sinchronizavimą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5420">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** - Is using modern hierarchy sync or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5444">**AppVersionMajor –** „Office“ programos pagrindinė versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5444">**AppVersionMajor -** The Major version of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5445">**AppVersionMinor –** „Office“ programos papildoma versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5445">**AppVersionMinor -** The Minor version of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5446">**AppVersionUpdate –** „Office“ programos komponavimo versijos peržiūra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5446">**AppVersionUpdate -** The Build Revision of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-5447">**CollectorVersion –** kliento rinkimo logikos versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-5447">**CollectorVersion -** A version identifier for the client collection logic.</span></span>

### <a name="officetelemetryvolumetrackingdata"></a><span data-ttu-id="bf211-6221">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6221">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-6222">Telemetrjos įvykių kiekio stebėjimo metrika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6222">Event volume tracking metrics for telemetry events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="bf211-6223">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6223">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6224">**EventThreshold** – didžiausias vieno įvykio egzempliorių, kuriuos galima išsiųsti laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6224">**EventThreshold** - The maximum number of instances of a single event that can be sent in a window of time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6225">**HighestEventCount** – didžiausias vieno įvykio egzempliorių, išsiųstų šiuo laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6225">**HighestEventCount** - The highest number of instances of a single event sent this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6226">**HighestEventName** – įvykio, kurio egzempliorių skaičius šiuo laikotarpiu didžiausias, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6226">**HighestEventName** - The name of the event with the highest number of instances in this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6227">**TimeWindowInSeconds** – laikotarpio trukmė sekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6227">**TimeWindowInSeconds** - The duration of the window in seconds.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6228">**TotalEvents** – bendras įvykių, išsiųstų laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6228">**TotalEvents** - The total number of events sent during the window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="bf211-6229">**UniqueEvents** – unikalių įvykių, išsiųstų laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bf211-6229">**UniqueEvents** - The number of unique events sent during a window.</span></span>
